     Interest Rates


          Pursuant to ยง15-1-4, the post judgment interest rates for the
          current and previous years are as follows. This rate does not apply
          to judgments based on contracts or statutes specifying a different
          interest rate.


     Calendar Year  Post Judgment Interest Rate
          1993                 5.72%
         1994                  5.61%
          1995                 9.22%
          1996                 7.35%
          1997                 7.45%
          1998                 7.468%
          1999                 6.513%
          2000                 7.670%
          2001                7.34% *
          2002                 4.28%

          * Between January 1, 2001 and June 14, 2001, the post judgment
          interest rate appearing on this page was erroneously reported as
          8.052%.


